{"word":"παρεπίδημος","slug":"παρεπίδημος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παρεπίδημος, ον</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, ἐπίδημος</el> ‘at home, visiting in a place’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπιδημέω\">ἐπιδημέω</a></el>; ‘residing as foreigner’] ‘staying as a resident foreigner’, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only as noun <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὁ\">ὁ</a> π.</el> <b>resident alien, sojourner <a href='B:650 11:13'>Hb 11:13</a>; <a href='B:670 1:1'>1 Pt 1:1</a>; <a href='B:670 2:11'>2:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παρέξῃ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παρεπίκρανα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}